    Gaussian quadrature points and weights

    normal_quadra.Rd

    Generate Gaussian quadrature points and corresponding weights

    normal_quadra(n, mm)

    Arguments

    n

    Number of quadrature points

    mm

    Absolute value of minumum or maximum of quadrature points

    Value

    A list of Gaussian quadrature points and corresponding weights

    Examples

    normal_quadra(41, 5)
#> $nodes
#>  [1] -5.00 -4.75 -4.50 -4.25 -4.00 -3.75 -3.50 -3.25 -3.00 -2.75 -2.50 -2.25
#> [13] -2.00 -1.75 -1.50 -1.25 -1.00 -0.75 -0.50 -0.25  0.00  0.25  0.50  0.75
#> [25]  1.00  1.25  1.50  1.75  2.00  2.25  2.50  2.75  3.00  3.25  3.50  3.75
#> [37]  4.00  4.25  4.50  4.75  5.00
#>
